<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="24.0">I heard about his death a day later from a volunteer for a group that donated money to survivors struggling to get by. Over the next few days, four friends of his invited me to his memorial service.</p>
        
    
                                  <aside
    data-pp-id="25"
    data-pp-blocktype="promo"
    data-pp-location="story promo"
    dir="ltr"
    class="bb-promo-story story-promo-group size04 right out02 wide-sm wrap | hide-print" >

    <div class="story-promo-group__logo user-level--0__show user-level--1__show">
