            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/the-secret-irs-files">The Secret IRS Files</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/lord-of-the-roths-how-tech-mogul-peter-thiel-turned-a-retirement-account-for-the-middle-class-into-a-5-billion-dollar-tax-free-piggy-bank">
                                    How Peter Thiel Turned a Retirement Account for the Middle Class Into a Tax-Free Piggy Bank
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Roth IRAs were intended to help average working Americans save, but IRS records show Thiel and other ultrawealthy investors have used them to amass vast untaxed fortunes.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/justin-elliott">Justin Elliott</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/patricia-callahan">Patricia Callahan</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/james-bandler">James Bandler</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2021-06-24EDT05:00">June 24, 2021, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

